title: Default values are not shown in 'Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: Default values are not displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
OB: The default values for the report parameters are not shown in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
EB: The default values for the report parameters should be displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog for any report that has default parameter values.
